import { makeStyles } from '@material-ui/core/styles'

export const useStyles = makeStyles(() => ({
  tabsContainer: {
    display: 'flex',
    borderRadius: 3,
    overflow: 'hidden',
    width: 'min-content'
  },
  activeMenu: {
    padding: '0 20px',
    height: '40px',
    background: '#f89523',
    color: 'white',
    textAlign: 'center',
    fontSize: '14px',
    display: 'flex',
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
    cursor: 'pointer',
    minWidth: 120
  },
  inactiveMenu: {
    padding: '0 20px',
    height: '40px',
    background: '#EEEEEE',
    color: '#7C8A97',
    textAlign: 'center',
    fontSize: '14px',
    display: 'flex',
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
    cursor: 'pointer',
    margin: '0 0.5px',
    minWidth: 120
  },
  text: {
    whiteSpace: 'nowrap',
    fontWeight: '500'
  }
}))
